<br />
<br />Since this is a decent place to ask, are there any viable SPC assemblers outside of spcas and the one included with WLA? I don't care for WLA's quirks and spcas is very limited.  If spcas was on par with xkas feature set it would be great for larger projects.  I've used spcas so far and it works, but it was for tiny SPC drivers where the lack of features isn't a big deal.

		

