		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Once you have a wavetable synthesizer, you just don't care anymore.  SNES, N64, GBA, MOD FILES, it's all the same.  Unless you're making music for a homebrew SNES game, you don't need to make SPC700 stuff.

		

		</td>
