	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I seem to remember it's 16 samples (one BRR block). But the trick is to resample all your waves such that the period is a multiple of 16 samples. For example, resample them such that middle C plays at 4186, 8372, 16744, or 33488 Hz, and all your loop lengths will be a multiple of 16, 32, 64, or 128 samples respectively.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


